    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) in a bowl with 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Drain, then add your <strong>king prawns</strong> and mix everything together – these are your <strong>marinated king prawns</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1657624031059-x200.jpg",
