            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once the butter has melted, add your <strong>tomato paste</strong> with your <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>ground cumin </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1657624086722-x200.jpg",
