            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1657624086722-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>marinated king prawns</strong> and cook for an initial 3 min</p><p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Once the prawns have had 3 min, add the <strong>reserved starchy pasta water </strong>and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> to the pan</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min further or until the prawns are cooked through and the sauce has thickened – these are your <strong>spicy king prawns</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1657624099394-x200.jpg",
