            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cooked conchiglie</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>charred corn</strong> to the spicy prawns and stir it all together until the pasta is fully coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>spicy king prawn conchiglie</strong></p><p>Season with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Crumble your <strong>feta</strong> over the <strong>remaining charred corn</strong>, add the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong> and mix together – this is your <strong>charred corn & feta</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
